properties.headline: Freeze Warning issued January 21 at 4:00PM EST until January 22 at 9:00AM EST by NWS Tampa Bay Ruskin FL
properties.description:
* WHAT...Sub-freezing temperatures as low as 30 possible.

* WHERE...Inland Pasco County.

* WHEN...From 1 AM to 9 AM EST Wednesday.

* IMPACTS...Freeze conditions could kill crops, other sensitive
vegetation. Remember to bring pets indoors.
properties.instruction:
Take steps now to protect tender plants from the cold. To prevent
freezing and possible bursting of outdoor water pipes they should
be wrapped, drained, or allowed to drip slowly. Those that have
in-ground sprinkler systems should drain them and cover above-
ground pipes to protect them from freezing.

NWSheadline: FREEZE WARNING IN EFFECT FROM 1 AM TO 9 AM EST WEDNESDAY
